txt.en: Sundered in battles long ago between Angmar and the Zhélruka, Tûr Fúar, the Drearspire looms over Câr Bronach like a twisted, skeletal talon. Within the tower's walls, dwarf-expedition supplies can be found. These supplies must have been captured and taken to Tûr Fúar. They should be collected and returned to the expedition.
Collect the stolen expedition supplies at Tûr Fúar
Sundered in battles long ago between Angmar and the Zhélruka, Tûr Fúar, the Drearspire looms over Câr Bronach like a twisted, skeletal talon.
Grúmachath can be found in central Câr Bronach.\n\nYou should bring the expedition supplies to Grúmachath.
Tûr Fúar, the Drearspire, can be found in central Câr Bronach.\n\nYou should collect the stolen expedition supplies found at Tûr Fúar.
